      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent demonstrates correct numerical implementation at the required spatial order.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification confirms second-order spatial accuracy for the incompressible Navier-Stokes implementation in the rotating reference frame. Observed order of accuracy is 1.97, consistent with the formal order of the discretization scheme. No implementation defects were identified."
