      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model and power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al. coefficients) are selected based on their established use in FDA pump hemolysis benchmarks. Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2; selection is justified by published benchmark participation."
